# English Comments & Docs Rule

## Requirements
- Write all code comments in English.
- Write all documentation (README/markdown, SKILL/RULE text, docstrings) in English.
- Avoid adding new Vietnamese (or any non-English) text in comments/docs.

## Examples
- Bad:
  - `// thêm skeleton vào component`
  - `/* đây là ghi chú */`
- Good:
  - `// Add skeleton to the component`
  - `/* This is a note */`

